    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2006-05-16</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2006-06-09T21:28:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p> Renewable Fuels Promotion Act - Amends the Petroleum Marketing Practices Act to prohibit a franchisor from restricting a franchisee from installing a renewable fuel pump on the franchisee marketing premises.</p> <p>Deems such restriction to be null and void and unenforceable under the Act.</p> <p>Amends the Energy Policy Act of 1992 to set a deadline for mandatory installation of at least one renewable fuel pump at every federal fleet fueling center in the United States.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
